    "body": "The simulated backed provides functionality similar to 'ganache'. It creates a separate blockchain where you can deploy your own contracts and interact with them, all from within Go code and without having to install/launch additional software.\r\n\r\nYou don't need to use it with your mainnet node's chaindata (and in fact I would not recommend it because it may alter the database).",
